data.description: Move right in to this charming colonial with 3 bedrooms, 2 full baths, central air, 1 car attached garage and fenced backyard. Enter into the living room with wood burning fireplace, large front window, laminate flooring, coved ceilings, and neutral paint. The dining room connects and flows with same flooring, charming built-in and attaches to the kitchen as well as the added on family room. Family room has carpet, tons of natural light with surrounding windows and sliding door out to the large backyard with patio, shed and motion sensor lights. The kitchen has same laminate floor, pantry space, brand new fan/light, newer '21 dishwasher, double sink with garbage disposal and all appliances stay. Upstairs you'll find the extra large master bedroom with walk-in closet and attic access, plenty of natural light and hardwood floors under the carpet. Two additional bedrooms, one with a bonus cedar closet and the other with a walk-out to the flat roof. Linen closet and a full bathroom with tub/shower round out the upstairs. The basement has a partially finished rec room with 2016 nature stone floor, glass block windows and studs ready for new drywall. The unfinished side has plenty of storage space, laundry area and utility sink, approximately 5 yr old washer and dryer stay. Don't miss the other full bathroom with walk-in shower in the basement! Updated GFCI outlets and new ceiling fans in 2023, New hot water tank in 2021. Arlo doorbell camera stays. You do not want to miss this one!
